title: The Coolest Places On Earth Series 1 02of22 Americas West Coast
description:
The Coolest Places on Earth: Series 1

Travel Documentary hosted by Rodger Leopardi, published by Bellum Films in 2015 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/e/e6/The-Coolest-Places-on-Earth-Series-1-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

The Coolest Places on Earth 
The Coolest Places on Earth takes viewers on a journey of discovery to the most astonishing places on the planet - cities, festivals, landmarks and jaw-dropping works of nature - exploring each location's history and culture, to discover why it deserves to be called one of the coolest places on earth!




2)  America's West Coast 
Today on the Coolest Places on Earth we're taking you on a road trip up America's Pacific coast from Los Angeles to Seattle and north to the rugged 49th state, Alaska. We'll see stars in Hollywood and high above the Redwoods, rip some breakers, mush a team, hook salmon alongside some grizzlies and-"belay on"-scale some big walls. So grab your gear, your board, and your appetite, because where we're going you'll need the fuel.
